articles.author: Minnie Chan
articles.title: US F-35 and Chinese J-20 fighter jets had close encounter over East China Sea, says US general - The Star Online
articles.description: Advanced Chinese and American fighter jets have had several encounters in the East China Sea, a source close to Beijing’s military told the Post, saying it reflected the high level of tensions between the two nations.
